data.description: Starr Lake is one of the most Sought-After Peaceful and Friendly Communities in Acworth. This is an incredible opportunity to live in this 6 bedroom 4 and a half bath 3 sided brick home. This home has a newer roof with a transferable warranty, newer deck and new carpet through-out.  Primary on the main with two separate walk-in closets, Open-concept living area seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining and family room. The kitchen has white quartz counter-tops with a center island, double ovens and stainless steel appliances. The expansive deck overlooks the wraparound driveway that provides ample parking for your guest. Plus a rear side garage to house an extra car, boat or toys. Starr Lake is a Swim & Tennis Community with a well-stocked lake for fishing and paddle boating.  Lake view and walking trails located 500 feet away. With Award winning Schools it’s Conveniently located to major highways, parks and restaurants. Just a quick 15 minute drive to Lake Allatoona Beach. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the beauty and charm for yourself. This property is agent-owned License #307046
